item.title: Help my fix my compile please
item.dc:creator: @Jump_On_Java Jump On Java
item.description:
@Jump_On_Java wrote:

Open Up Client.Java, Right Click Compile.Bat And Select Edit. Highlight It All And Delete It, Then Paste This Into Your Compiler.Bat -

@Echo Off Title Your Compiler Color 0F @Echo Compiling .. "C:\Program Files\Java\Jre1.5.0_09\Bin\Java.Exe" server Pause

If This Doesn’t Work Private Message Me.
